电涉事门店，工作人员表示确实出现了老鼠，但过多细节不愿透露。同日，中山市三角镇政府相关负责人回应，三角镇市场监管分局已对该涉事餐厅开展检查，责令其立即整改，并采取“回头看”，确保其整改落实到位。 在黑猫投诉发布的2024年度线下餐饮机构领域红黑榜榜单中，杨国福麻辣烫位列黑榜第一。 惊现老鼠，全部下架！杨国福突然被曝！曾冲刺麻辣烫第一股_门店_投诉_整改"},"attached_info":"CkEI052fpP+J+uFqEAMaCTExNDA3MzUzOSCN7u2+BjAAOB5ADXILMTUzOTIwNTk0NTh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"88 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b1d3444a65802b6077e60f1b90e5bdb6_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"14_1742649906.413694","card_id":"Q_15439452568","target":{"id":15439452568,"title":"刘慈欣为什么没写过伤痕文学？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/15439452568","type":"question","created":1742476316,"answer_count":45,"follower_count":73,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[665,666,48770],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"刘慈欣出生于1963年，按时间来算“那几年”应该贯穿了他的整个青少年时期，更糟糕的一点是他还出生于知识分子家庭，1966年，刘慈欣的父亲失去设计院工作，被下放到山西阳泉挖煤。刘慈欣被送到河南老家逃避灾难，小学二年级才到阳泉和父母团聚，正常情况下，这段童年经历应该会在小孩子心里留下很大的记忆吧 另外补充一点，伤痕文学在我这里不是贬义词，只是很好奇作家的童年经历应该会对日后文学写作有很大的影响吧"},"attached_info":"CkEI052fpP+J+uFqEAMaCTExNDA4NDgwMiCcqPC+BjAAOElADnILMTU0Mzk0NTI1Njh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"84 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-7aef7e681437e9d6d361ab8208697275_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1742649906.414400","card_id":"Q_39167242","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":39167242,"title":"有哪些建筑看上去让你觉得很吃惊？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/39167242","type":"question","created":1451926557,"answer_count":780,"follower_count":37570,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":""